      <div class="about-text">
        <div class="section-tag">About the Conference</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Africa's Premier Finance & Banking Summit</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <p>The MAIDEN International Conference of Finance and Banking (ICFB) 2026 is a landmark academic and professional gathering hosted by the Department of Banking and Finance, Faculty of Administration and Management Sciences, University of Calabar.</p>
        <p>The conference brings together scholars, practitioners, policymakers, and industry leaders from across Africa and beyond to advance critical discourse on digital transformation, financial inclusion, and economic resilience.</p>
